Name: Jaden & Jasmine: The Curse of Deception
About the game: Follow a high school student named Jaden Black who's on the run from the government. Jasmine Miles who's hired by the CIA is sent after him to kill him. But the task isn't as easy as she thought it would be. (FREE DLC) Content: Includes another story following 3 boys Chris, Hakeem and Tyler each of them have their own story with CHOICE DECISIONS what you choose may affect their lives rather they live or die or something else. Play Villainess Situations to find out their story. 'This game is a visual novel based off the book series which shares the same title as the game.'
